reviewText: Pretty good movie selection. No technical issues with media. Great value.

The movies are all great movies and even the lessor known movie *Body of Lies* is still pretty good. Now my biggest con/ drawback of ordering this set is the way the movies are arranged. Yes, you get all 4 movies, however they are stacked in sets of 2 on top of each other. My Aviator disc had several scratches and skipped about 30-45 seconds of the movie (not a huge deal). Yet, the packaging is less than ideal, I have already removed 2 discs and put them in additional sleeves that I owned.

Leo is by far one of the top actors of today. These 4 titles will not disappoint. I will rank them in order of awesomeness. They are all awesome don't get me wrong. Here it goes: Blood Diamond, Shutter Island, Body of Lies, and The Aviator. My opinion but any true Leo fan will get this asap.
